00:27:21,999 --> 00:27:25,082
(lively piano music)

427
00:27:32,001 --> 00:27:35,918
There we go, and a few
little sticks over here.

428
00:27:42,144 --> 00:27:45,532
Okay, but you see what you
can do in just a few minutes

429
00:27:45,532 --> 00:27:49,199
with an almighty brush
and an almighty knife

430
00:27:50,324 --> 00:27:51,885
and a beautiful painting in your heart.

431
00:27:51,885 --> 00:27:54,322
All you have to do is let it out.

432
00:27:54,323 --> 00:27:55,823
A few more sticks.

433
00:27:59,586 --> 00:28:02,526
There we go, I think
we'll call that finished,

434
00:28:02,526 --> 00:28:04,968
and I wanna thank you very,
very much for watching us.

